		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Is it common for others to switch back and forth between solid white and a fine grid? Is there a standard test procedure that I can cite in that test's help page, analogous to the SMPTE standard defining color bars? If you are the only person who would use that feature, it would probably be better as a stand-alone ROM.<br /><br />But if anyone else expresses interest, I could add Select to switch between solid color screen and a fine line grid.

		

